    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable door dings, some paint fading on the hood, and a few scuffs on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and the driver's seat shows significant wear, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need new brakes and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that reflects its mileage and years on the road.",
