    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance with everyday comfort. This car has been my reliable daily driver, and it shows in the smooth, responsive handling and the quiet confidence of the engine. The exterior maintains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather seats are supple with no tears, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracks. All interior electronics, including the premium sound system, navigation, and heated seats, are in full working order. Mechanically, this car is sound, having followed a strict maintenance schedule. Recent service includes a fresh oil change, new air filters, and a brake inspection confirming plenty of life left in the pads. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you're ready for the road immediately. This is an honest, well-cared-for vehicle looking for its next home.",
